You will perform the role of platform engineering, i.e. application platforms, such as SAP (e.g. BASIS), Rapid Application Development (e.g. Outsystem), Mobile Infrastructure and Database (e.g. Oracle, SQL).

Requirements:
• Proficient in IT, e.g. Database, WebMethods Integration, Operating Systems, Application Servers (e.g. WebLogic), SAP Basis, Network &amp; Infrastructure.
• Qualification in IT or Engineering